This paper deals with voting rules and their manipulation, which falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). The use of mathematical proofs and analysis suggests that it could also be classified under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The study of voting systems and their properties could also be considered a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
